text: Three Young Texans is a 1954 American western movie directed by Henry Levin and starring Mitzi Gaynor, Keefe Brasselle, Jeffrey Hunter, Harvey Stephens, Aaron Spelling. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1954 movies Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Henry Levin
